ratnosint7 is an open-source reconnaissance orchestration engine that integrates and coordinates the following third-party open-source tools. Each tool retains its own license and copyright. See THIRD_PARTY_TOOLS.md for detailed attribution and license information.

Integrated Tools (13):

Passive + Active:
- subfinder (OWASP Project Discovery)
- amass (OWASP)
- findomain (Findomain Project)
- sudomy (Screetsec)
- tugarecon (skynet0x01)

Passive Only:
- assetfinder (Tom Hudson)
- sublist3r (Aboul3la)
- subscraper (m8sec)
- turbolist3r (fleetcaptain)
- dome (v4d1)
- as3nt (Cinerieus)
- substr3am (Nexxai)

Active Only:
- dnsx (OWASP Project Discovery)

